---
title: Pan-Seared Greek-Style Double Salmon with Roasted Potatoes and Yogurt Sauce
description: Lemon-pepper spiced salmon, roasted potatoes and creamy tzatziki – what more could you want for dinner? Zesty green beans? You've got it!
